query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mi_idx it2) NoMergeJoin(it2 mi mi_idx mc) NoNestLoop(it2 mc mi mi_idx ct) NoHashJoin(ct it2 mc mi mi_idx cn) NoMergeJoin(cn ct it2 mc mi mi_idx t) NoMergeJoin(cn ct it2 mc mi mi_idx t it1) */ select min(mi.info) AS budget,
min(t.title) AS unsuccsessful_movie
from movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
inner join info_type AS it2
on mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'bottom 10 rank'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind IS NOT NULL AND ( ct.kind = 'production companies' OR ct.kind = 'distributors')
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND ( t.title like 'Birdemic%' OR t.title like '%Movie%') AND t.production_year > 2002
inner join info_type AS it1
on mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'budget';
